{"timestamp": "2025-12-07 06:01:49.194244", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission successful.\n\n- Anomaly detected: Yes\n- Faulty device(s): web_server_0 (10.200.0.3)\n- Root cause: sender_application_delay\n\nRationale:\n- L3/OSPF, DNS, and load balancer are healthy with normal RTTs and success rates.\n- ICMP to web_server_0 is normal, excluding path issues.\n- Severe HTTP connect delays and high start-transfer times isolated to web_server_0 from multiple vantage points, including same VLAN.\n- apache2 inactive on all web servers; only web_server_0 exhibits degraded HTTP behavior, indicating an application-layer issue on that host.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 1978, "output_tokens": 134, "total_tokens": 2112, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1408}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
